SUMMARY:The Toronto PATH and Lunch
DESCRIPTION:GTA Hiking & Stuff\nCome and join us for a walk through the PA
 TH\, Toronto's underground pedestrian walking network.\n\nWe're doing some
 thing different while the forest trails start to transition from winter to
  summer.\n\nWe will meet at Union Station in the Great Hall (see pic). We 
 will make our way north to the Eaton Center. From there\, we will head sou
 th\, completing a loop as we make our way to The Old Spaghetti Factory ([h
 ttps://www.osf.com/](https://www.osf.com/)) for a late lunch. We will make
  changes to the route in order for us to arrive at the restaurant on time 
 (2pm).\n\nPlenty of breaks along the way and if you haven't attended one o
 f our events before\, come out and meet the group.\n\nThe PATH is a mostly
  underground pedestrian walkway network in downtown Toronto that spans mor
 e than 30 kilometers of restaurants\, shopping\, services\, and entertainm
 ent accommodating more than 200\,000 business-day commuters as well as tou
 rists and residents.\n\nFor more information\, visit:\n[https://www.toront
 o.ca/explore-enjoy/visitor-toronto/path-torontos-downtown-pedestrian-walkw
 ay](https://www.toronto.ca/explore-enjoy/visitor-toronto/path-torontos-dow
 ntown-pedestrian-walkway)\n\n**LEGAL DISCLAIMER AND LIABILITY INFORMATION:
 **\nBy RSVP'ing and paying the event fee (if applicable)\, you are confirm
